(1, 'Sabir Muhammed', 'Kottarakara, Kollam, Kerala, India', '', 'Sabirmuhammed95@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:40', 'I see the world through the camera. When I was a kid, my dad gave me a camera and I used to toy around with it a lot. Later, it became a part of me. The pictures I take are the frozen moments in time that vanishes in a second. Pixelbug has provided me with an opportunity to prove and practice my passion.', '14/11/1995', 'https://www.facebook.com/sabir.muhammed.3?fref=ts', 'https://m.facebook.com/sabirmuhammedphoto/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=9.0016637 76.8001776&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|9.0016637 76.8001776', '08'),
(2, 'SP Ganeshan', 'Kumarpara, Guwahati, Assam, India', '', 'ganeshansp931@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:40', 'My first incident with photography was when I took a picture of my brother. Everyone liked the picture so much that I started clicking more photographs! Over the years, it has become more of a passion than a hobby. Being in Pixelbug has been a wonderful experience as I not only get a platform to polish my photography skills, but also because I get many opportunities to teach people and learn from them. ', '15/10/1994', 'www.facebook.com/ganeshan.sp.75', 'www.facebook.com/ganeshanphotography', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=26.1701107 91.7330285&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|26.1701107 91.7330285', '07'),
(3, 'Jenkins Jose Shirley', 'Verkilambi, Kanyakumari, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'jenkinsjose@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:40', 'I started clicking pictures from my sixth grade onwards, which slowly developed into a hobby. After joining Pixelbug, I learned a lot of new techniques in photography like double exposure, focal zoom long exposure etc. widening my knowledge from Nature and Landscape Photography. I have also learnt about different lenses and their unique features. ', '23/09/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/jenkinsjoseshirley', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=8.2953483 77.2924254&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|8.2953483 77.2924254', '10'),
(4, 'Adhithyan S', 'KK Nagar, Trichy, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'admkr.2010@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:41', 'From the first time I saw a camera, I became intrigued and I wanted to know more about it. I was fascinated by how a small device can take such an awesome picture and I started to experiment with it. Pixelbug gave me all the equipment I needed to enhance my knowledge in photography. ', '01/07/1997', 'https://www.facebook.com/adhi.dharman', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=10.7574385 78.6910413&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|10.7574385 78.6910413', '11'),
(5, 'Saathwik Chandan', 'Hyderabad, Andhra Pradesh, India', '', 'saathwikjst4u@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:41', 'Photography is an art. Art can be developed through a group of similar minded people. I found that in Pixelbug. We don''t take a photograph, we make it! This was rooted in our brains. Now, Pixelbug is growing like never before! And as always, "We don''t believe in time, we believe in timing!" ', '08/10/1994', 'www.facebook.com/saathwikjst4u', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=15.1283849 79.1766114&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|15.1283849 79.1766114', '01'),
(6, 'P Saiteja ', 'Annanagar, Chennai, India', '', 'pattalasaiteja@gmail.com ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:42', 'Photography has always fascinated me. The photos don''t always turn out the way you want them to, and that is what is beautiful. It''s unpredictable, and that''s what makes me take out my camera and explore. And only by exploration do we stumble upon new things and learn. Pixelbug is a platform for me to do the same with like-minded people. ', '02/04/1998', 'https://www.facebook.com/SaiTeja.1000?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0891361 80.2095622&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0891361 80.2095622', '30'),
(7, 'Priya Soundar', 'Bangalore, Karnataka, India', '', 'priyasoundar.17@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:42', 'When I first joined Pixelbug, I didn''t have as much knowledge about photography as I have now. It has given me a lot of exposure and wonderful opportunities to learn.', '17/08/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/priya.soundar.3?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=12.9715987 77.5945627&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|12.9715987 77.5945627', '13'),
(8, 'Raghu Govind Pillai', 'Trivandrum, Kerala, India', '', 'govind1612@hotmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:43', 'From what started out as a camera for a birthday gift, to becoming a hobby turned passion, photography has been one of my keen interests for years now. Starting out by taking auto-focused shots of sceneries, to now manually focusing to follow my required ideology, photography is like an art to me, framing memories that occur rarely/frequently, making them last forever. Joining Pixelbug, and becoming a part of the team, I''ve managed to practice my skills and at the same time, learn more from the talented team of individuals within.   ', '16/12/1996', 'https://m.facebook.com/raghu.the.rebel.govind.pillai', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=8.5241391 76.9366376&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|8.5241391 76.9366376', '14'),
(9, 'Arun Prakash R', 'Neyveli, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'arunprakash782@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:43', 'I had started taking interest in Photography recently and it''s not been a year yet but I have learnt a lot bacause of Pixelbug. Pixelbug is teaching me new things everyday. I think Pixelbug will help me grow into a good photographer.', '05/09/1996', 'https://m.facebook.com/arun.prakash.5996?ref=bookmarks', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=11.5432364 79.4760133&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|11.5432364 79.4760133', '29'),
(10, 'Sanjana Pedada ', 'Hyderabad, Andhra Pradesh, India', '', 'sanjana9998@gmail.com ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:44', 'I started loving photography ever since I clicked few nature pics during an outing with my friends. I decided to apply to be part of Pixelbug at that moment. Induction process gave me my first DSLR experience! I started imagining how every beautiful thing I come across can turn into more of an adorable picture. Every day that I spend with Pixelbug gives me more insight into photography, adding on to the process of my learning! ', '09/09/1998', 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100009678734489&__nodl', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=15.1283849 79.1766114&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|15.1283849 79.1766114', '28'),
(11, 'Lavanya Kumaran', 'Ganapathy, Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'lavanyakumaran275@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:44', 'Being part of Pixelbug has been the best experience of my college life. Every artist was first an amateur. Wildlife photography is what piqued my interest in this field. I have been able to explore other types of photography as well by being part of this incredible club filled with people of similar interests. Pixelbug is and will always be family to me :) \n\nThere are no rules for good photographs, there are only good photographs.', '27/05/1995', 'https://www.facebook.com/lavanya.kumaran.7', 'https://www.instagram.com/lavanya_lavender/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=11.0422275 76.9815877&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|11.0422275 76.9815877', '06'),
(12, 'Varun Elangovan', 'Tiruvanmiyur, Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 's.e.varun@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:44', 'My photography journey started in the second semester of college when I realised that I have an interest in taking photographs and can take good ones too. Pixelbug provided me the right platform to develop my skills and follow my passion. I have learnt a lot being a part of it, apart from just photography. Pixelbug is really close to my heart.', '05/09/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/varun.elango.16', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=12.9830269 80.2594001&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|12.9830269 80.2594001', '12'),
(13, 'Shilpa Sweth', 'Koorkanchery, Trissur, Kerala, India', '', 'shilpasweth@gmail.com ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:45', 'My interest in photography began on a family trip. It was my first major vacation and I felt inclined to preserve all the beautiful sights on a more trustworthy memory device than my scatterbrained-self. But on joining Pixelbug, I started to not only enjoy taking pictures of interesting things but also enjoyed trying to view something mundane from a more unusual perspective with all the different camera tricks my friends showed me. My photography tends to be more of a hit or miss but I continue to enjoy taking pictures.', '19/08/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/shilpa.sweth?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=10.5025308 76.2088012&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|10.5025308 76.2088012', '15'),
(14, 'Joseph John', 'Vytilla, Cochin, Kerala, India', '', 'Josephlkg@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:45', 'Photography got me interested when I realised that I have to preserve the places I visit. Pixelbug has been a fun learning experience for me. Meeting some great people. We might run into many hurdles but we always find a way out. Being a part of this club will always be my pleasure.', '01/05/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100008373661751&fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=9.9666543 76.3168134&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|9.9666543 76.3168134', '16'),
(15, 'Siranjeevi D', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'mmanojsira@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:46', 'I had developed a basic interest in nature and structural photography during the past 2 years. Pixelbug proved to be a right platform for me to improve my skills and develop my passion.', '04/11/1996', 'facebook.com/xmenmanoj', 'https://www.flickr.com/photos/siranjeevid/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '17'),
(16, 'Jagathi Harshitha A', 'Guntur, Andhra Pradesh, India', '', 'jagathiharshitha.arumalla@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:46', 'Photography is the best way to showcase the beauty of nature and the best moments happening around us. Pixelbug has given me a great chance to improve my photography skills and the way I look at things happening around. ', '01/01/1998', 'www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100004325629046', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=16.3066525 80.4365402&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|16.3066525 80.4365402', '27'),
(17, 'Nivedita Suresh ', 'Teacher''s colony, Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'tangled16797@gmail.com ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:47', 'I have always liked freezing moments and collecting them. It all started like that. They say a camera is a save button for the mind''s eye. Well, true that. For me, it has always been a great art where one has got little to do with the things we see and everything else to do with the way we see them. I thought it was the only language that can be understood anywhere in the world. I fell prey for the love of macro photography. I started from scratch and could take some decent pics. My heart finally had what it wanted. My eyes started seeing in the most beautiful way ever. I really thank Pixelbug for letting me grow more and more towards what I love the most. Eagerly waiting to learn more. Waiting for an ocean of opportunities to knock on. Thank you :)', '16/07/1997', 'https://www.facebook.com/nivedita.suresh.3', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.1303882 80.2467688&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.1303882 80.2467688', '26'),
(18, 'Abdul Basith Mohamed Ali', 'Gomathipuram, Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'abdulbasith96@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:47', 'Photography, to me, is freezing time. A way of rolling back reality. A virtual time machine, if I dare say that. Giving a person the power to relive thier special and important instants in life; to let them feel the emotions of that moment again, is something very beautiful. \n\nPixelbug has not only given me the opportunity to do this, but has taught me how to do this better. ', '30/10/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/ab.wajela?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=9.9239376 78.1578683&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|9.9239376 78.1578683', '18'),
(19, 'Lalitha Rani Anapu', 'Rajahmundry, Andhra Pradesh, India', '', 'anapulalitharani@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:47', 'I discovered my interest in photography only when I started watching the show, Nat geo cover shot: Maximum city, but I''ve never given it a serious thought. I started working towards it only when my friends told me that I''ve an eye for photography and that I compose pictures well. Pixelbug has given me the chance to work with a DSLR for the first time. So, I''ll always be grateful for that one wonderful first exeperience.', '27/04/1998', 'https://www.facebook.com/lalitharani.anapu', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=17.0005383 81.8040345&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|17.0005383 81.8040345', '24'),
(20, 'Danish Ali', 'Phoenix Bay, Port Blair, Andaman', '', 'dannieboi0@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:48', 'A macro shot of a bee on a flower is the one shot which made me very interested in photography. Photography is not only my hobby, but also my way out of this competitive and busy life. It helps me to express my views in different ways. Pixelbug has been a perfect platform to showcase my skills and improve them.', '14/09/1995', 'https://facebook.com/danish.ali.1806?refid=8', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=11.6718253 92.7350582&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|11.6718253 92.7350582', '19'),
(21, 'Swarthika P', 'Trichy, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'swarthika.sweet@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:48', 'Inevitably, I started to see the beauty in everything around me and capturing it. Ever since I got a camera, I''ve been clicking pictures and I enjoy the infinite possibilities in my passion. With constant support from my friends, family and Pixelbug, I''ve improved a lot and will keep learning.', '02/04/1996', 'https://m.facebook.com/swarthika.sweet', 'https://m.facebook.com/littleinfinity02/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=10.7904833 78.7046725&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|10.7904833 78.7046725', '20'),
(22, 'Rounak Sarkar', 'Nagpur,Maharashtra, India', '', 'rounak1811@yahoo.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:49', 'My interest in photography developed when i first shot my cousin''s wedding from my friend''s camera and everyone praised about it. Pixelbug helped me to improve my passion by carefully looking into my work and correcting my mistakes.', '18/11/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/rounak.sarkar.1426?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=21.1458004 79.0881546&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|21.1458004 79.0881546', '25'),
(23, 'Venkata Krisshna N', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'venkat.krisshna@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:49', 'Photography has always been one of my favorite hobbies. When I was using a digicam, I wondered how the different modes and settings affected the image. Having understood that, I moved onto a DSLR and basked in the freedom to control what my images look like. I like to shoot portraits and candids and love to induce architecture and geometry in my photographs. Pixelbug has offered me such opportunities and many more which has enabled me to further explore my interest. My time in Pixelbug will remain the most memorable experience of my undergrad life!', '21/08/1995', 'facebook.com/venkatkrissh', 'instagram.com/venkatkrissh', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '04'),
(24, 'Abhishek Shankar', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'abh241096@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:50', 'I really don''t have much to say. Pixelbug Rocks! \n', '24/10/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/abhishek.shankar24?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '21'),
(25, 'Vijay', 'Madurai,Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'vijay.n2468@ gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:50', 'I''m very much interested in photography because of the various techniques like light painting, focal zoom,etc. Photography has helped me to capture golden memories. Pixelbug provides me a healthy platform to pursue my area of interest.', '31/08/1997', 'https://www.facebook.com/vijaynatarajan.n2?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=9.9252007 78.1197754&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|9.9252007 78.1197754', '23'),
(26, 'Sanjay Kumar Tudu', 'Navi Mumbai, Maharashtra, India', '', 'prince.jay.san@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:51', 'I generally do Portraits and Architectural photography. Pixelbug has given me a chance to practice my skills at campus. The lighting and angles are challenging. Indoor shoots, like at Barn hall, gives us a nice test to quickly change settings on the fly.', '06/10/1995', 'www.facebook.com/Prince.jay.san', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=19.0330488 73.0296625&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|19.0330488 73.0296625', '22'),
(27, 'Lakshmi K Ajayan', 'Thrissur, Kerala, India', '', '179.lakshmi@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:51', 'I started clicking photographs when I was twelve when my dad bought me my first point-and-shoot camera. I was greatly motivated by the Photography Club in my school. I recently realised that even as a kid back then, rule of thirds and composition techniques were something that came naturally to me, even without having known it in theory. I enjoy clicking flora, streets, landscapes and wallpaper-like pictures. After my point-and-shoot got stolen, I didn''t have the guts to ask for a new camera, until I was inducted into Pixelbug. The members gave me immense support and I have come this far because of the opportunities Pixelbug has given me. ', '17/09/1994', 'www.facebook.com/lakshmi.k.ajayan', 'www.flickr.com/photos/112034977@N06/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=10.5276416 76.2144349&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|10.5276416 76.2144349', '03'),
(28, 'Pradeep Kumar V B', 'Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'vbkumar1995@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:51', 'Being a Nature lover, I was initially captivated by birds. Slowly, my interest towards photography was born when I saw photographs posted by eminent wildlife photographers on Facebook. I started my photography journey with just a digital camera and right before joining Pixelbug, I got my first DSLR Canon 1100D. Bird photography was extremely challenging with the limited equipments that I had, but the joy in capturing a single frame of any bird was immeasurable. After interacting with the pool of talented photographers in Pixelbug, I also grew an affinity towards candid, street and action photography, which implicitly helped me in wildlife photography. With my new lens and a FB page, I plan to plant curiosity about wildlife in many hearts through my photographs, indirectly helping in conservation.', '25/01/1995', 'https://www.facebook.com/pradeep.kumar.108889', 'https://www.facebook.com/Beaks-and-Wings-530425883782915/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=11.0168445 76.9558321&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|11.0168445 76.9558321', '02'),
(29, 'Apuroop Mandala', 'Hyderabad, Telangana, India', '', 'apuroopmandala.aav@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:52', 'I started liking Photography when i first saw some motion capture clicks online. Then, the journey started with a small Canon digital camera. Never missed a moment there after! Fortunately, my interest and those magical moments my digicam gave me, got me into Pixelbug. But once i was into the club ,that liking towards photography has turned to loving it and I am deeply in a relationship with it right now ! :D The guidance the club has provided me in just a year is something which i wouldnt have gotten in few years of self-exploration. We are a family and photography is our language.', '07/04/1996', 'https://facebook.com/apuroop.prince', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=17.385044 78.486671&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|17.385044 78.486671', '05'),
(30, 'Jonath Dinesh ', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'niftyd007@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:52', 'I have a strong passion towards photography. With a vague idea of how to take good pictures, I entered college. During Festember , I came to know about the Pixelbug team. When I saw their pictures, I was simply amazed. They were never just a group of people but a family with a will to give their best always. I feel great to be part of this family now. Only if u have the passion, you will have the urge to learn. I can proudly say that I''ve got a family to teach me. \n', '07/06/1996', 'https://m.facebook.com/jonath.dinesh?ref=bookmarks', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '31'),
(31, 'Gowtham Mahesh', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'm.gowtham.m.m@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:53', 'Going through the induction process to get into Pixelbug was the most interesting experience I''ve ever had. I''m learning lot more than I had ever thought and met new people. ', '24/10/1997', 'https://www.facebook.com/gowtham.magesh?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '32'),
(32, 'Praveena Devi', 'Trichy,Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'praveena9522@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:53', 'When I first saw the photos my friends took back then in high school, I was fascinated and that''s how my interest in photography started.That proud moment when you click a picture after so much patience and the happiness you gain when people comment on your pictures are priceless. Pixelbug has given me the opportunity to explore the true art of photography. It''s an amazing platform for me to learn and improve.', '22/10/1995', 'https://www.facebook.com/praveena.devi.5', 'https://www.facebook.com/Praveenas-Photography-1539731879689521/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=10.7904833 78.7046725&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|10.7904833 78.7046725', '33'),
(33, 'Aashish Bohra ', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'aashishbohra17@gmail.com ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:53', 'I started shooting when a small Kodak digicam was gifted to me in my 9th grade. I started with Macro and Travel photography and also a little bit of light painting. Now, with a D5200, I feel I''ve still learnt only a little of what photography is. Pixelbug has and will be a great platform for photographers.\n', '17/06/1995', 'https://m.facebook.com/ashishbohra1995?ref=bookmarks', 'https://m.facebook.com/aashishbohraphotography/?ref=bookmarks', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '34'),
(34, 'Nirmal B Pillai', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'nirmal.briju@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:54', 'My interest in photography took a major leap when my cousin first gave me his old DSLR. I was fascinated by the way it could alter reality and make things look more appealing just by the magic of framing and light control. Pixelbug is a great platform to discuss and practice photography! ', '09/09/1997', 'https://m.facebook.com/nirmalstrider?ref=bookmarks', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '35'),
(35, 'Rahul Nair', 'Trivandrum, Kerala, India', '', 'rsnair95@hotmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:54', 'I started clicking pics on my dad''s digital camera and got fascinated by the idea of capturing the small details of this beautiful nature and see through different perspectives. Later on, I moved to a DSLR and photography became my favorite hobby. Every time I click a picture, I learn something new about photography. Pixelbug has provided me with the opportunity to cover various events and explore more in the field of photography.', '30/03/1995', 'https://www.facebook.com/rahume?fref=ts', 'https://www.instagram.com/rahulsnair95/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=8.5241391 76.9366376&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|8.5241391 76.9366376', '36'),
(36, 'Habeeburahman C A', 'Ernakulam, Kerala, India', '', 'habeeb831@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:55', 'I used to travel and take many photos. I love capturing the scenes. My friends'' criticism and their constant support bring up the photographer in me. I slowly started to read about photography, cameras, lenses etc.\nPixelbug is a platform for me to evolve. All the members are amazing photographers. I want to gain experience and information as much as possible, by contributing to the club.', '30/06/1993', 'https://www.facebook.com/habeeb.rahman.3781?fref=ts', 'https://m.facebook.com/Habeebs-Photography-174882716239130/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=9.9816358 76.2998842&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|9.9816358 76.2998842', '37'),
(37, 'Kamala Kannan', 'Chidambaram, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'kamal.rocks.you@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:55', 'I have been clicking photos with my DSLR in Auto mode for a long time. After I joined this college, I learnt how to take photos in Manual mode. It helped me express a lot more things and look at things differently, from which my passion for photography started. Pixelbug is providing me with the oppurtunity to improve my skills. The members teach me new things. But apart from all that, Pixelbug has been family to me and has taught me lessons about friendship, love and trust, which is really valuable. ', '02/08/1997', 'https://m.facebook.com/kamala.kannan.3726?tsid=0.9490174035449981&source=typeahead', 'https://m.facebook.com/kkcanon600d/?ref=bookmarks', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=11.3981936 79.6953594&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|11.3981936 79.6953594', '38'),
(38, 'Pratyush Dikshit', 'Gorakhpur, Uttar Pradesh, India', '', 'pratyushdikshit.pd@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:55', 'I started clicking photos to capture the beautiful moments happening in and around my life in order to arrange them in a ledger full of memories. I like travelling, taking adventurous trips and interacting with people. Pixelbug has provided me with a platform to bond with photography. It has provided me with opportunities to capture various events in college, outside the campus, streets, markets, beaches, forests etc.The journey as a photographer in Pixelbug cannot be explained in words.It has been an awesome experience of Learning-with-Fun in this club. Moreover, this is not only a photography club but a family of passionate photographers.', '26/07/1992', 'https://www.facebook.com/pratyush.dik', 'https://www.facebook.com/PDs-Photography-1136983612988043/', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=26.7605545 83.3731675&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|26.7605545 83.3731675', '39'),
(39, 'Saravanan Vasanth', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'saravanan2127vasanth@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:56', 'Photography has shown me a whole new perspective of life. The colors and shapes fascinate me. It helps in capturing a moment that is going to stay close to you for the rest of your life. Photography is a way of expressing one''s feelings. Pixelbug has paved the right path for me to reach my destination :)', '21/06/1997', 'https://www.facebook.com/sara.2127?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '40'),
(40, 'Devika Joshi', 'Mumbai, India', '', 'devika.joshi9497@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:09:25', 'My interest in photography developed when I was in the 9th grade I think. I had read about trick photography and I started trying it out on my phone''s camera. Since then, I''ve developed an interest in this art. \nPixelbug has given me an opportunity to nurture my interest and learn so much more. I am extremely lucky to be a part of it.', '09/04/1997', 'https://www.facebook.com/devika.bieber.3?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=19.0759837 72.8776559&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|19.0759837 72.8776559', '41'),
(41, 'Ganesh Kumar A', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'aganeshkumar6696@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:56', 'Since I do paintings, I wanted my own reference images and I realised that photography makes this easier and gives several other ideas for my paintings. Photography has made my way of seeing things different, perspective-wise, which I can implement in my paintings. Pixelbug helps me in knowing more about these different types of photography. ', '06/10/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/ganesh.agan.10?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '42'),
(42, 'Reesha Arul', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'reeshaarul@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:57', 'Photography is my way of expressing thoughts. Pixelbug is the perfect place to showcase your talent and learn more about photography. ', '13/04/1996', 'https://m.facebook.com/reesha.arul?ref=bookmarks', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '43'),
(43, 'Ishan Bodele ', 'Bhilai, Chhattisgarh, India ', '', 'Ishanbodele@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:57', 'I started on my journey in photography from a very young age. I was fascinated by the SLR camera my dad used to click photos in. My curiosity and my dad''s knowledge about cameras and photography, in general, led me into learning about this amazing technology. From clicking photographs during family vacations to practicing new techniques during events, festivals, I learned more and more about photography. Pixelbug has provided me with an amazing platform to practice my passion in college. ', '22/01/1996', 'https://m.facebook.com/ishan.bodele?ref=bookmarks', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=21.1938475 81.3509416&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|21.1938475 81.3509416', '44'),
(44, 'Abhishek Vinod', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'vinod.abhishek96@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:57', 'What really inspired me to take up photography was my dad telling me that I have a good eye for detail when he saw a few photos I had clicked with a point and shoot. Pixelbug has been a wonderful learning platform!', '19/04/1996', 'facebook.com/ab.vinod', 'facebook.com/AbhishekVPhotography', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '45'),
(45, 'Akshaya Selvakumar', 'Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', '1209akshaya@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:58', 'I got to know the photographer in me when I got my new mobile after joining college. Passion started with mobile photography and when you have very good posers as friends, you get extra practice. After joining Pixelbug, my skills have become better not just from changing from auto mode to manual mode, but more than that. I''ve gotten more practice and learned a lot.', '12/09/1995', 'https://www.facebook.com/akshaya.pinto?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=9.9252007 78.1197754&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|9.9252007 78.1197754', '46'),
(46, 'Mohini Rao', 'Jagdalpur, Chhattishgarh, India', '', 'g.mohini17@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:58', 'I started my photography journey from my orientation programme in the first year of college. I came to know about this photography team then. I wanted to learn more and thus applied to join the club and now I love being in this club and photography more than anything. Pixelbug gave me a platform to learn and gain knowledge about the art of photography. I feel lucky to be part of this club and make many sweet memories. ', '17/11/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/mohini.rao.10?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=19.0740973 82.008014&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|19.0740973 82.008014', '47'),
(47, 'Charu Joshi', 'Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India', '', 'Zosycharu@gmail', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:58', 'When I was in class 11, my father bought a DSLR. I got fascinated by photography since then.I used to take photos of flowers and sceneries. After coming to college, I came to know about Pixelbug where I can learn more and grow more towards pursuing my interest.', '05/12/1997', 'https://www.facebook.com/charu.joshi.98?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=26.2389469 73.0243094&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|26.2389469 73.0243094', '48'),
(48, 'Cliff David Beck ', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'cliffghostrider@gmail.com ', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:59', 'I became interested in photography when I clicked some candids of people in my hometown. I had borrowed a camera from my friend then. Both of us had a knack for photos. Pixelbug has provided me with an amazing platform to practice my passion. ', '07/02/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/cliff.d.beck?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '49'),
(49, 'Karthik Venkatachalam', 'Sullurpeta, Andhra Pradesh, India', '', 'karthikav97@gmail.com', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:06:59', 'At first, I was not interested in photography and was not a good photographer either but once I got to know about Pixelbug and when I saw the pictures taken by the members, I was really amazed and excited to learn the techniques from them. I have come to know different types of photography and I hope to learn more and become a good photographer.', '06/06/1997', 'https://www.facebook.com/karthik.venkatachalam.39?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.70215 80.0180717&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.70215 80.0180717', '50'),
(50, 'Akshay Ganesh', 'Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India', '', 'akshayganesh@yahoo.co.in', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-06-05 02:07:00', 'My interest in photography grew when I started painting. It allowed me to realise how much can be expressed through an art form. I started off with mobile phone photography. Later, moved on to a DSLR. Pixelbug has given me more opportunities to explore different fields in photography. I learnt a lot from the tasks that were given and I have the chance to gain knowledge from my peers who are experts in each field.', '16/08/1996', 'https://www.facebook.com/akshay.ganesh.1481?fref=ts', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=13.0826802 80.2707184&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|13.0826802 80.2707184', '51'),
