(53, 'Taha Kamalam Elangovan', 'Trichy, Tamil Nadu, India ', '', 'taha.elan@gmail.com', '2016-06-05 02:23:31', '2016-06-05 02:23:35', 'Very few things can evoke instant happiness and satisfaction within us. A good photograph is one among them. I experienced that when I first started clicking pictures randomly after watching a friend of mine do the same. Soon, I started to see the beauty of it all. I''ve been in love with photography ever since. ', '1997-06-25', 'https://m.facebook.com/taha.kam.25', '', 'https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=10.7904833 78.7046725&zoom=8&size=400x500&maptype=roadmap&markers=color:red|10.7904833 78.7046725', '54');
